# Rules: packages/annotator (sp-annotator)

## Directory Mapping (Upstream -> SP Fork)

При синхронизации с upstream Plannotator:

| Upstream | SP Fork |
|----------|---------|
| `packages/server/` | `src/server/` |
| `packages/shared/` | `src/shared/` |
| `packages/ui/` | `ui/` |
| `packages/ui/config/` | `ui/config/` |
| `packages/editor/` | `editor/` |
| `packages/review-editor/` | `review-editor/` |

Upstream `apps/` (hook, opencode-plugin, marketing, vscode-extension) НЕ портировать.

## SP-Specific Code (не перезаписывать)

- `src/ai/` — весь AI layer (Claude Agent SDK, SessionManager, endpoints)
- `review-editor/components/AITab.tsx`, `AskAIInput.tsx`, `AIConfigBar.tsx`, `PermissionCard.tsx`
- `review-editor/hooks/useAIChat.ts`
- `ui/components/AnnotationToolbar.tsx` — кнопка "Ask AI"
- `ui/utils/aiProvider.ts`, `ui/utils/aiSetup.ts`
- `ui/hooks/useAgents.ts`

## Import Conventions

- Relative imports, НЕ workspace aliases
- `@plannotator/shared/...` -> `../shared/...` или `../../src/shared/...`
- `@plannotator/ui/...` -> `../../ui/...`

## Branding

- User-facing строки: "sp-annotator" (не "Plannotator")
- package name: `@sp/annotator`
- Storage keys: `plannotator-identity` (для совместимости с upstream)
- Config path: `~/.plannotator/` (для совместимости)

## Build

```bash
cd packages/annotator
bun install
bun run build          # build:review -> build:plan -> build:cli
bun run dev:plan       # dev server port 3000
bun run dev:review     # dev server port 3001
bun test               # run tests
```

## Testing Checklist

- `bun run build` — без ошибок
- `bun test` — все тесты зелёные
- `./bin/sp-annotator annotate <file.md>` — annotation UI открывается
- `./bin/sp-annotator review <file.md>` — approve/feedback кнопки видны
- `./bin/sp-annotator diff` — git diff в review UI
- `grep -r "Plannotator" ui/ editor/ review-editor/ --include="*.ts" --include="*.tsx"` — только в LICENSE/attribution

